
<view class="wrap g-vip-page">
    <image
        mode="widthFix"
        src="{{src$.bg}}"
    ></image>
    <view class="content">
        <view class="input-box">
            <view class="ul">
                <view
                    class="li"
                    wx:for="{{arrData}}"
                    wx:key="{{index}}">
                    <text>{{item}}</text>
                </view>
            </view>
            <input
                maxlength="6"
                bindinput="bindInput"
                data-item="{{formData.Code}}"
                value="{{formData.Code.value}}"
                type="number"
            />
        </view>
        <button
            bindtap="handleSubmit"
            class="g-button button"
        >立即激活</button>
    </view>
    <view class="popup" wx:if="{{isPopup}}">
        <view class="popup-inner">
            <text class="popup-title">您的服务包状态</text>
            <text class="popup-title">待激活</text>
            <view class="popup-content">
                <text class="popup-prompt">我的们控糖顾问将在1个工作日内</text>
                <text class="popup-prompt">与您联系请注意接听电话，谢谢</text>
            </view>
            <button
                bindtap="handleRoot"
                class="popup-button"
            >知道了</button>
        </view>
    </view>
    <view class="footer">
        <view class="bg"></view>
        <view class="prompt">
            <text>如果您已购买专业版套餐，但尚未拿到激活码</text>
        </view>
        <view class="prompt">
            <text>请联系天猫客服 021-31227952 </text>
        </view>
        <view class="prompt">
            <text class="color">（周一至周五 9：00-18：00）</text>
        </view>
    </view>
</view>
